6.1 How to use the PKCS11 module
================================

     $ cat > ~/.soft-pkcs11.rc <<EOF
     mycert	cert	User certificate	FILE:/Users/lha/Private/pkinit.pem
     app-fatal	true
     EOF
     $ kinit -C PKCS11:/usr/heimdal/lib/hx509.so lha@EXAMPLE.ORG



